trans-unit.source: Contains methods and properties that are used to manage queries to the tracking data that is contained in the SQL database used by a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller metoder och egenskaper som används för att hantera frågor till spårningsdata som finns i SQL-databasen som används av en <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] SqlTrackingQuery provides methods and properties that you can use in order to access certain kinds of tracking data stored in a SQL database by the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]SqlTrackingQuery innehåller metoder och egenskaper som du kan använda för att komma åt vissa typer av spårningsdata som lagras i en SQL-databas i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>

trans-unit.source: Access to this data is provided through <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects.
trans-unit.target: Åtkomst till den här informationen anges via <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objekt.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A> to try to get a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> for a specific workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan anropa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A>att hämta en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>för en viss arbetsflödesinstans.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.TryGetWorkflow%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can call <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A> to get a collection of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects that correspond workflow instances that have tracking data that matches a set of query parameters contained in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> that is passed as a parameter to the method.
trans-unit.target: Du kan anropa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A>att hämta en uppsättning <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>objekt som motsvarar arbetsflödesinstanser som har spårningsdata som matchar en uppsättning fråga parametrar finns i en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions>som skickas som en parameter till metoden.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A>

trans-unit.source: See the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> class for more information about the kind of tracking data available and see the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> class for more information about the kind of queries that can be performed.
trans-unit.target: Finns det <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>klass för mer information om vilken typ av spårningsdata är tillgänglig och se den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions>klass för mer information om vilken typ av frågor som kan utföras.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>
